{"word":"σφαγιάζομαι","slug":"σφαγιάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σφαγιάζομαι</b></el> <el>(σφαγιάζομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σφάγιον'><el>σφάγιον</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to slay a victim, sacrifice</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:—hence aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>σφαγιασθείς</el>, <i>slain, sacrificed</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}